er Sandy in the background.\n* Lana\'s capture of Sandy marks the longest time between a {{ashfr|main character}}\'s first and second captures, at 99 episodes.\n* {{Ash}} and {{Rotom}} narrate the preview for the [[SM100|next episode]].\n* This is the first time during the {{series|Sun and Moon}} when the [[Who\'s That Pokémon?]] segment features a Pokémon that has already been featured in said segment earlier in the series. In this case, {{p|Salandit}} was featured in \'\'[[SM008|Lillie\'s Egg-xhilarating Challenge!]]\'\'.\n\n===Errors===\n\n===Dub edits===\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Epilang|color=90BDDC|bordercolor=F1912B\n|zh_cmn={{tt|伊布要去哪裡呢？為了見那孩子哪裡都能去！|Eevee, Where Are You Going? To Go Anywhere to Meet Up With That Kid!}}\n|nl={{tt|Wij weten waar jij naartoe gaat, Eevee!|We know where you are going, Eevee!}}\n|he={{tt|!אנחנו יודעים לאן אתה הולך, איבי|We Know Where You\'re Going, Eevee!}}\n|ko={{tt|이브이 어디 가? 그 애를 만나러 어디까지라도!|Eevee, Where Are You Going? To Go Anywhere to Meet Up With That Kid!}}\n|pt_br={{tt|Sabemos para onde está indo, Eevee!|We know where you\'re going, Eevee!}}\n|es_la={{tt|¡Bienvenido, Eevee!|Welcome, Eevee!}}\n|es_eu={{tt|¡Eevee, Sabemos a Dónde Vas!|We Know Are You Going, Eevee!}}\n}}\n{{-}}\n{{EpicodePrevNext|\nprevcode=SM098 |\nprevtitle=Bright Lights, Big Changes! |\nnextcode=SM100 |\nnexttitle=Battling the Beast Within! |\nseries=Sun & Moon series |\ncolorscheme=Alola}}\n{{Project Anime notice}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1038}}\n[[Category:Sun & Moon series episodes|099]]\n[[Category:Episodes written by Aya Matsui]]\n[[Category:Episodes storyboarded and directed by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes storyboarded by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes directed by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes animated by Osamu Murata]]\n[[Category:Episodes animated by Shūhei Yasuda]]\n[[Category:Episodes by multiple animation directors]]\n[[Category:Episodes focusing on Lana]]\n[[Category:Episodes in which a main character\'s Pokémon learns a new move]]